---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy — Dynasty Desk">
  <Nav />
  <main class="bg-white py-16 text-gray-900 md:py-24">
    <article class="prose prose-lg mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">
      <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-navy md:text-4xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <section class="mt-10 space-y-8 text-base leading-relaxed text-navy/80">
        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-display text-xl font-bold text-navy">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p>
            Dynasty Desk is a mobile football franchise management simulation game operated by
            Big North Marketing LLC, a company registered in Texas, United States. This Privacy
            Policy describes how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our
            application and related services.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-display text-xl font-bold text-navy">2. Information We Collect</h2>
          <ul class="ml-4 list-disc space-y-2">
            <li>
              <strong>Email address</strong> — collected when you create an account, authenticated
              via Supabase.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Gameplay data</strong> — stored locally on your device using IndexedDB.
              This data stays on your device unless you opt in to cloud sync.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Cloud sync data</strong> — if you enable cross-device sync, your gameplay
              data is stored securely in our cloud infrastructure powered by Supabase.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-display text-xl font-bold text-navy">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <ul class="ml-4 list-disc space-y-2">
            <li>Account authentication and management</li>
            <li>Cross-device cloud synchronization of your game data</li>
            <li>Service improvement and analytics</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            We do not sell your personal data to third parties.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-display text-xl font-bold text-navy">4. AI-Generated Content</h2>
          <p>
            Dynasty Desk uses Google's Gemini API to generate in-game narrative content,
            including articles and game summaries. Your gameplay data may be sent to Gemini
            to generate these stories. No personal identifying information is included in
            these requests.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-display text-xl font-bold text-navy">5. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>
            Your account data is retained for as long as your account is active. You may
            request deletion of your account and associated data at any time by emailing
            <a href="mailto:support@dynastydesk.app" class="text-gold-dark underline">support@dynastydesk.app</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-display text-xl font-bold text-navy">6. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <ul class="ml-4 list-disc space-y-2">
            <li>
              <strong>Supabase</strong> — used for account authentication and optional cloud
              sync of game data.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Google Gemini</strong> — used to generate in-game AI narrative content
              such as articles and game summaries.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-display text-xl font-bold text-navy">7. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            Dynasty Desk is not directed to children under 13 years of age. We do not
            knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we learn that
            we have collected personal information from a child under 13, we will take steps
            to delete that information promptly.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-display text-xl font-bold text-navy">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted
            on this page with an updated revision date. We encourage you to review this page
            periodically.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-display text-xl font-bold text-navy">9. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
            <a href="mailto:support@dynastydesk.app" class="text-gold-dark underline">support@dynastydesk.app</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </article>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>
